{"tid":2286880,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"NBC News話拜登靠拉丁裔選民贏阿利桑那州","createTime":"2020-11-15T10:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T14:00:02.000Z","uid":67896,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3df9075af87d5931e379ebac9b7f2e4bbb976838","tid":2286880,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T10:36:42.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-small\">睇之前講明先，NBC藍到仆街，有份cut鳩侵侵白宮直播</span><br />\n<br />\n懶人網址<a href=\"https://twitter.com/NBCNews/status/1327906949887893504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNBCNews%2Fstatus%2F1327906949887893504&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=66accdc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNBCNews%2Fstatus%2F1327906949887893504&h=eb1aebf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/NBCNews/status/1327906949887893504</a><br />\n原文網址<a href=\"https://www.nbcnews.com/news/latino/years-making-established-latino-groups-helped-biden-arizona-nevada-n1246864?cid=sm_npd_nn_tw_ma\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fnews%2Flatino%2Fyears-making-established-latino-groups-helped-biden-arizona-nevada-n1246864%3Fcid%3Dsm_npd_nn_tw_ma&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=f2d53ca7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nbcnews.com/news/latino/years-making-established-latino-groups-helped-biden-arizona-nevada-n1246864?cid=sm_npd_nn_tw_ma</a><br />\n<br />\n情況有啲似香港<br />\n阿利桑那 = 九龍東<br />\n拉丁裔 = 新移民<br />\n拜登 = 民建聯<br />\n<br />\n第一段講移民政策做成嘅歧視，令拉丁裔不滿共和黨<br />\n後面兩三段都係講民主黨靠今場選舉有足夠嘅椿腳幫手拉票<span class=\"x-small\">同埋唔知幾多嘅種票</span><br />\n令到佢地拉丁裔得票率好高<br />\n<br />\n你話有冇出古惑，大家心知肚明<br />\n死人投票、120%投票率、逾時投票，同香港嘅一屋三姓十三人投票一樣<span class=\"x-small\"><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2011年香港區議會選舉種票風波\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F2011%E5%B9%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E7%A8%AE%E7%A5%A8%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BHHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=11853b0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/2011年香港區議會選舉種票風波</a></span><br />\n但係捉賊拿唔到贓，就好難推翻個賽果<br />\n<br />\n有冇住阿利桑那嘅巴打解答下真唔真，啲Latino係咪好憎GOP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6d09a3c6b35a32d10204ffab24ac6d11fbdba3","tid":2286880,"uid":295230,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T10:40:56.000Z","msg":"拉丁裔一定憎trump既話咁florida係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且根據暫時既選民資料黎睇，trump既全國拉丁裔支持度都係有較大幅度既提升"},{"pid":"318630edab79f56dd34236d5fdc42dbe5f25b6df","tid":2286880,"uid":67896,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"0b6d09a3c6b35a32d10204ffab24ac6d11fbdba3","tid":2286880,"uid":295230,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T10:40:56.000Z","msg":"拉丁裔一定憎trump既話咁florida係咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且根據暫時既選民資料黎睇，trump既全國拉丁裔支持度都係有較大幅度既提升"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T10:47:27.000Z","msg":"成王敗寇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 贏左就可以咁樣吹水<br />\n雖然仲未知係咪真係贏左Arizona"},{"pid":"32deac6bf619319639bde36b3c28ceb5956131ad","tid":2286880,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T13:26:07.000Z","msg":"如果真係有造假，咁點要搵個解釋去自圓其說，與其話拉丁裔，不如話得罪McCain仲合理"},{"pid":"bbae4654b9eebfd0dfc91c830312dc3a32d417e7","tid":2286880,"uid":67896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"32deac6bf619319639bde36b3c28ceb5956131ad","tid":2286880,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T13:26:07.000Z","msg":"如果真係有造假，咁點要搵個解釋去自圓其說，與其話拉丁裔，不如話得罪McCain仲合理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"